Area Loss Prevention Manager - 1 Opening(s) at null
Posted by: null
Posted date: 29-Apr
Job Description:Interface with the Area Operations Team to create awareness about SLP compliance
Prevent, detect, and resolve all incidents of shoplifting, transactional fraud, of internal, external malicious activity.
Engage in the process of analyzing, monitoring, detecting and resolving discrepancies in inventory holdings of the store.
Carry out audits of cash, inventory, and financial transactions, exchanges, and reconciliation processes across all stores in the assigned area.
Skillful deployment of the tools and strategies utilized for combating theft and fraud such as overt and covert CCTV, DVRs, EAS, Security Fixtures, and monitoring of key items, assets, and departments.
Collect local intelligence and assist key store leadership during times of threat or crisis to minimize risks to life and property.
Assuring that departments and areas conduct a daily perpetual inventory of key high shrinkage items and conducting root cause analysis when there are discrepancies in the counts.
Identify existing or potential risk exposures unique to the local environment and executing counter measures to the same.nullnullnull
